{
  "stem": "5911.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember being sent to a wall-- completely flat like a board.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when they asked your name, instead of-- my mother gave, naturally, their name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Instead of saying that I am 10, she told them I am 12, because they would have seen how they registered me flat like a board.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But as soon as we were out of the examining room and showers, we were given clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were not given prisoners clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In-- when we meant-- went to Stutthof, I saw women completely shaved and in prisoners clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There where a lot of Hungarian Jews in Stutthof-- tremendous amount.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were-- and they had numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't have time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You see, we got there in July of '44.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They didn't have time to do all those things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When my mother went to pick up clothes-- I remember as today-- she took a brown little jacket that didn't look for a little girl.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It looked more--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--more mature; a skirt and clumpen, like shoes that would make high-- taller a little bit, and a bra.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember telling her, what do I need a bra?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I mean, look at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She stuffed my bra with paper, and she told them that I'm 12 years old. 12 years old is a mature kid.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what I mean? 12 years old, because she had the feeling that the children, again, are going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we slept in barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Showers before, before we got dressed-- to showers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, my mother was a nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they asked-- they-- she helped out in the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it was bad in the ghetto, then Stutthof was worse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the ghetto at least we had our own little place, even a cubicle.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
